Please cite new paper:
- Engelhardt BE, Srouji JE, Jordan MI, Brenner SE (2010)

Original paper available at PLoS Computational Biology:
- Engelhardt BE, Jordan MI, Muratore KE, Brenner SE (2005) Protein Molecular Function Prediction by Bayesian Phylogenomics. PLoS Comput Biol 1(5): e45

ICML paper describing newer version of the model available on BE's website:
- Engelhardt, BE, Jordan, MI, Brenner SE (2006) A statistical graphical model for predicting protein molecular function. Proceedings of the International Conference on Machine Learning (accepted).